channel.title: Requesting a Profesional Website Logo/favicon!
channel.description:
Hey guys, first time back in over 6 months. i am currently making a website for a customer (has nothing to do with rsps/games) i was wondering if anyone here is interested in making a logo for me.
[url=http://www.uniquevipevents.com.au]http://www.uniquevipevents.com.au[/url]
If you are could you please take note this is a entertainment/event planning website.
Colors: -Black -Purple -Orange
I would like it to suit the website as much as possible. i do not want any cheap looking logo that was made in paint in 5 minutes.
Also if your very keen making a Favicon aswell. This will also have no Link/Name directing back to you or this site. but i will owe you a favour when you need one.
